  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bb5\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd - \u0b95\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Teaching activities without holidays from tomorrow till November - Ministry of Education",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Education has decided to carry out teaching activities without holidays from the first day of August to the coming November in schools across the country.",
        "However, the Ministry of Education has also announced that teaching activities will take place in schools only 3 days a week, as was the case last week.",
        "Accordingly, advice has been given to carry out teaching activities in schools only on Mondays, Tuesdays and Thursdays and to carry out virtual teaching activities on Wednesdays and Fridays.",
        "It has been decided to carry out teaching activities in schools from August to the coming November without any holidays in view of the scholarship examination for the students of class 5 and the general education standard high standard examinations.",
        "It has been decided to conduct the scholarship examination for this year on 27th November and the high level examinations from 27th November to 23rd December. Accordingly, the teaching activities will be carried out from Monday to November without holidays.",
        "A report has been requested regarding the evaluation of the learning ability of the students who will go to the 3rd standard without complete education in the 1st and 2nd classes and how to advance their next level of teaching.",
        "In addition to Susacheriya school bus service, private buses will be introduced to transport school students under the name of 'Patasalai Seva' and it is expected to be implemented nationwide soon."
      ],
